ActFisheries Act
SubjectRegulations Amending the Alberta Fishery Regulations, 1998
PrecisRegulations Amending the ALBERTA FISHERY REGULATIONS, 1998 in order to (1) update the necessary Schedules to include Tiger Trout as a species that can be regulated as a game fish in Alberta; and (2) amend the Regulations to allow the use of dip nets, minnow traps, and seine nets to harvest Virile Crayfish in Alberta.
